    "chemicalDescription": [
      "Polyurethane-18 is a complex polymer formed by the reaction of m-tetramethylene diisocyanate, polybutylene glycol and Dimethylolpropionic Acid (q.v.) The pre-polymer is neutralized with Triethylamine and condensed with a combination of hydrazine and C1-8 diamines to achieve chain extension."
